deployhttpd.yml
first created a Deployment "deployhttpd.yml"
here kind of this Deployment is "Deployment"
in which replica is set to 1 that means one pod is always running , replica set will create a new pod if the existing pod is terminated or deployed
label is set to "deployment"
container "c00" is running httpd
--------
service.yml
An then a service is created using yml "service.yml"
here kind of this service is "Service"
name of this service is "demoservice"
selector name is defined as "deployment" , which means this service will be applied to any Pod which has the label "deployment"
type of this service is "ClusterIP", which is applied only within the cluster
port number for this service is set to 80, and the target port is also 80


